and `destroy` actions for an indirected subsystem of Puppet. Valid termini for
this face include:

* `<%= face.class.terminus_classes(face.indirection.name).join("`\n* `") %>`

<% end # indirection
   end # notes or indirection
   unless face.authors.empty? -%>
